---
const appUrl = 'https://app.biashara-pos.com';
---
<section class="hero hero-vision">
  <div class="wrap hero-center">
    <div class="brand-lockup reveal"><b>Biashara</b><i>POS</i></div>
    <div class="tagline reveal" data-en="Smart Business · Seamless Sales" data-sw="Biashara Bora · Mauzo Rahisi">Smart Business · Seamless Sales</div>
    <h1 class="reveal" data-en='One POS. <span class="grad">Every business.</span>' data-sw='POS moja. <span class="grad">Kila biashara.</span>'>One POS. <span class="grad">Every business.</span></h1>
    <p
      class="hero-sub reveal"
      data-en='Sell, manage stock and see your <b>real net profit</b> after every sale — built for clothing, retail, restaurants, hospitals &amp; pharmacies. <span class="sw">Biashara zako, mfumo mmoja.</span>'
      data-sw='Uza, simamia stoki na uone <b>faida halisi</b> baada ya kila mauzo — imejengwa kwa nguo, rejareja, migahawa, hospitali na maduka ya dawa. <span class="sw">Biashara zako, mfumo mmoja.</span>'
    >Sell, manage stock and see your <b>real net profit</b> after every sale — built for clothing, retail, restaurants, hospitals &amp; pharmacies. <span class="sw">Biashara zako, mfumo mmoja.</span></p>
    <div class="hero-cta reveal">
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href={appUrl} data-en="Start for Free →" data-sw="Anza Bila Malipo →">Start for Free →</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="#preview" data-en="See it in action" data-sw="Iangalie ikifanya kazi">See it in action</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-ticks reveal">
      <span class="tick"><span class="ic">✓</span><span data-en="Phone, POS terminal & computer" data-sw="Simu, terminal ya POS &amp; kompyuta">Phone, POS terminal &amp; computer</span></span>
      <span class="tick"><span class="ic">✓</span><span data-en="Works offline" data-sw="Inafanya kazi bila intaneti">Works offline</span></span>
      <span class="tick"><span class="ic">✓</span><span data-en="TRA-compliant receipts" data-sw="Risiti zinazokubalika TRA">TRA-compliant receipts</span></span>
      <span class="tick"><span class="ic">✓</span><span data-en="Flat monthly fee" data-sw="Ada ya mwezi tu">Flat monthly fee</span></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
